Ruby Blackjack
====================

A commandline version of Blackjack written in Ruby.

How to play
=======
Step 1: cd to the directory of play_blackjack.rb

Step 2: issue 'ruby play_blackjack.rb' to play

Step 3: enter a bankroll when prompted: e.g. 1000

Step 5: place your bet: e.g. 100

Step 6: play your hand

Step 7: smile when you win!

	

